data.description: This Oak Lawn beauty boasts 5 bedrooms and 3 baths and sits on a 75 x 125 lot, the 2,843 square feet span across all three levels. Inside, you'll find gleaming hardwood floors, contemporary paint, and a welcoming living room adorned with recessed lighting. The formal dining area seamlessly connects to a spacious gourmet eat-in kitchen equipped with white shaker cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, and a breakfast bar.    The main level features a fully updated bath and a master bedroom with a beautiful stone fireplace. Ascending to the second level, you'll discover three sizable bedrooms, one of which boasts vaulted ceilings, along with a modern full bath showcasing a white vanity and custom tile work. The finished basement adds to the allure with a roomy family room illuminated by recessed lighting, a fifth bedroom, a fully updated bath, a laundry room, and a newer drain tile system.    Outdoors, the property offers an amazing yard enclosed by a privacy fence, complemented by a deck and a pool. Alley access leads to a two-car garage, and a separate concrete parking slip on the south side accommodates 3-4 cars. Recent updates include a new fence and pool in 2019, along with a complete renovation in 2018. Conveniently located near Oak Lawn Community High School, Premo's, Metra, downtown Oak Lawn, parks, shopping, and quick access to I-294
